    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#26406\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">apologize</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>1590年代，“为...辩护”； 见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of apology \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/apology\">apology</a> + <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ize\">-ize</a>。1725年出现了“遗憾地承认”的意义。希腊语的等效词 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">apologizesthai</i> 仅意味着“说明”。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Apologized</i>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">apologizing</i>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">apologizer</i>。</p>"
    }
